@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@token = {{token}}
@parentId = 7

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

### Create folder at root (200)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/folders
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "folder_name": "Tài liệu học kỳ 1"
}

### Create folder inside parent (200)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/folders
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "folder_name": "Bài tập",
  "parent_folder_id": {{parentId}}
}

### Missing folder_name (422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/folders
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "parent_folder_id": 1
}

### Invalid/non-owned parent (404)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/folders
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "folder_name": "Tài liệu học kỳ 2",
  "parent_folder_id": 999999
}

### folder_name too long (422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/folders
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "folder_name": "aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa"
}
